text: Michelle [ mi-shel ] is a female given name. The name was originally the French feminine form of Michael, meaning "who is like God?". Michelle is also a last name. This name was ranked #394 on the US Popular Names in 2021. People named Michelle include Michelle Pfeiffer, Michele Steffin and Michelle Obama. Fictional characters include Michelle Tanner from the sitcom Full House. == People == * Michelle Obama, Lawyer and Former First Lady of the United States * Michelle Pfeiffer, American actress * Michelle Jenneke, Australian athlete and model ==References== Category:Given names
title: Michelle (name)
